      "versionNonce": 556718857,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755062706797,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "So if backend need to access the\ndatabase, it first need to connect or hit request to\nlocalhost machine's 27017 which maps to docker container\nof database 27017 which is indirect process if not use networks",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "So if backend need to access the\ndatabase, it first need to connect or hit request to\nlocalhost machine's 27017 which maps to docker container\nof database 27017 which is indirect process if not use networks",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "EfQVXtzprXvjKX3VrpZF6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3630.047712928647,
      "y": 2013.9286963612617,
      "width": 1332.88330078125,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0e",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1612222089,
      "version": 351,
      "versionNonce": 1205215433,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1755062887610,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "So no portmapping, but in development if we want to connect ot database using mongo\ncomapss then we need a localhost port that mapp to so just put it in docker-compose file\nbut when in production, remove that for security purpose that no localhost get access to it only\ndocker networks",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "So no portmapping, but in development if we want to connect ot database using mongo\ncomapss then we need a localhost port that mapp to so just put it in docker-compose file\nbut when in production, remove that for security purpose that no localhost get access to it only\ndocker networks",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
